    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "es tew ſchodeen pawehſu / tu un\ntawi Behrni / no wiſſas tawas\nSir̈ds / un no wiſſas tawas\nDwehſeles.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tas KUNGS taws\nDeews nogreēſihs tawu Zeetu-\nmu/ un apſchehloſees pahr tewim/\nun atgreesiſees / un ſapulzinahs\ntew no wiſſeem Laudim/ us kur-\nren tas KUNGS taws Deews\ntew irr iſkaſijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jepſchu arridsan tawi Js-\ndſiktee patt Debbes Gallā buhtu/\ntad tomehr tas KUNGS taws\nDeews tew no turrenes ſapul-\nzehs / un neins tew no turrenes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS taws\nDeews weddihs tew us to Sem-\nmi / ko tawi Tehwi eemantejamā\nTeesā irr turreiſchi/ un tu eeman-\ntoti winnu / un wiſſch Darrihs\ntew labbi / un wairohs tew wai-\nrak ne ka tawus Tehwus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS taws\nDeeivs avgraiſihs tawu Sir̈di/\nun tawa Dſimmuina Sir̈di / ka\ntu to KUNGii tawu Deeivu mih-\nle no wiſſas tawas Sir̈ds/ un no\nwiſſas tawas Dwehſeles/ ka tu\ndſihwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS taws\nDeews liks wiſſus ſchohs Lahſtus\nus taweem Eenaidneekem/ un us\nteem/ kas tew cenihſt/ kas tew irr\nwajajſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tu atgreesiſees un klaui-\nfifi ta KUNGA Balkfnei / un\nDarriſi wiſſus winna Bauſlus/ ko\neſtew ſchodeen pawehſu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS taws\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Deews tew fohti wairohs wiſſa\ntawā Rohku Darbā/ pee tawas\nMeeſas Augteem/ un pee tawas\nLohpu Augteem/ un pee tawas\nSemmes Augteem eeſſch Labbu-\nma/ jo tas KUNGS atgreesi-\nſees/ ka tas pahr tew preezajahs/\ntew par labbu/ ittin ka wiſſch irr\npreczajees pahr taweem Teh-\nweem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad tu ta KUNGA ta-\nwa Deewa Balkfnei klauiſiſi/ un\nturreſi winna Bauſlus/ un win-\nna Likkunus/ kas ſchāi Bauſli-\nbas-Grahmata rakſtitiiirr/ kad tu\natgreesiſees pee ta KUNGA ta-\nwa Deewa ar wiſſu tawu Sir̈di/\nun ar wiſſu tawu Dwehſeli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ſchts Bauſlis / ko es-\ntew ſchodeen pawehſu/ tew ne irr\npaſlehpts/ tas arri ne irr tahtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas ne irr Debbeſi/ ka tu\nwarretu faazziht: kurſch no mum-\nkahps Debbeſi / ka wiſſch te-\nmuns dabbu / un leek mums to\ndsirdeht/ ka mehs to darram.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas arri ne irr wiinxpuſe\nJuhras/ ka tu warretu faazziht:\nKurſch no mums pahrzelſees win-\npufs Juhras/ ka wiſſch mums to\ndabbu/un leek mums to dsirdeht/\nka mehs to darram.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas Wahrdē irr foht-\nti tuwu pee tepw / tawā Mutte-\nun tawā Sir̈di/ ka tew to buhe-\ndarriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Reds/ es tew ſchodeen eſ-\nimu preekſchlizzis to Dſihwibu-\nun to Labbu/ ir to Nahwi un to\nLaunu.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
